== 製作 ==
2012年11月，執行製片人[[吉勒摩·戴托羅|吉勒摩·戴托羅]]說已經完成了幾部續集的草稿，而導演[[克里斯·米勒|克里斯·米勒]]想把鞋貓帶到異國情調的地方冒險<ref>{{cite news|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|title=Guillermo del Toro Talks PUSS IN BOOTS 2, KUNG FU PANDA 3 & TROLLHUNTERS; Says PANDA 3 Has the "Most Formidable Villain in the Series"|url=http://collider.com/puss-in-boots-2-sequel-kung-fu-panda-3-guillermo-del-toro/210271/|accessdate=2012-11-12|newspaper=Collider.com|date=2012-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318041406/http://collider.com/puss-in-boots-2-sequel-kung-fu-panda-3-guillermo-del-toro/210271|archive-date=2014-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年4月，鞋貓的配音員[[安東尼奧·班德拉斯|安東尼奧·班德拉斯]]說續集才剛剛開始製作<ref>{{cite web|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|title=Antonio Banderas Says He Just Started Work on PUSS IN BOOTS 2|url=http://collider.com/puss-in-boots-2-news-antonio-banderas/|publisher=Collider.com|accessdate=2014-04-16|date=2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417003227/http://collider.com/puss-in-boots-2-news-antonio-banderas/|archive-date=2014-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年6月12日，宣佈片名為《鞋貓劍客2：九條命和四十大盜》（{{lang|en|Puss in Boots 2: Nine Lives & 40 Thieves}}），並計劃於2018年11月2日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/madagascar-4-release-date/ |title=DreamWorks Animation Release Dates Include Madagascar 4 |publisher=Collider.com |date=2013-11-20 |accessdate=2014-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615042435/http://collider.com/madagascar-4-release-date |archive-date=2014-06-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

兩個月後，宣佈電影延遲至2018年12月21日在美國上映<ref name=CSShiftsTwo>{{cite web|title=DreamWorks Animation Shifts Two Sequels Back Slightly|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=122167|publisher=ComingSoon.net|accessdate=2014-08-22|date=2014-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140824140252/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=122167|archive-date=2014-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月，電影在公司重組和夢工廠動畫公司每年上映兩部電影的新政策下被砍<ref name="BOMNewDates2017-01-27">{{cite web|title=New Dates & Changes|url=http://boxofficemojo.com:80/schedule/?view=changes&p=.htm|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2017-04-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150127074138/http://boxofficemojo.com/schedule/?view=changes&p=.htm|archivedate=2015-01-27|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2015/01/dreamworks-animation-restructuring-to-cut-500-jobs-with-290m-charge-1201355918/|last=Lieberman|first=David|title=DreamWorks Animation Restructuring To Cut 500 Jobs With $290M Charge|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-01-22|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150125032539/http://deadline.com/2015/01/dreamworks-animation-restructuring-to-cut-500-jobs-with-290m-charge-1201355918/|archive-date=2015-01-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩個月後，班德拉斯採訪時透露，劇本正在重組，而且史瑞克可能會出現在電影裡<ref>{{cite news|last1=de Semlyen|first1=Phil|title=Shrek To Return For Puss In Boots 2?|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43826|accessdate=2015-03-28|work=Empire|date=2015-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401131146/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43826|archive-date=2015-04-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年11月6日，據《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》報導，{{le|克里斯·梅勒丹德利|Chris Meledandri}}將擔任《[[史瑞克5|史瑞克5]]》和《鞋貓劍客2》的執行製作人，而原配音陣容將回歸飾演各自的角色<ref name=ShrekReboot>{{Cite news|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/shrek-puss-in-boots-reboot-1203020785/|title=‘Shrek,’ ‘Puss in Boots’ Getting Rebooted (EXCLUSIVE)|author=Variety Staff|date=2018-11-06|work=Variety|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106210745/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/shrek-puss-in-boots-reboot-1203020785/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ShrekRebootAnimation>{{cite web|title=‘Shrek’ & ‘Puss in Boots’ Rebooting at Universal with Chris Meledandri|url=http://www.animationmagazine.net/features/shrek-puss-in-boots-rebooting-at-universal-with-chris-meledandri/|website=Animation Magazine|access-date=2021-01-24|date=2018-11-06|archive-date=2018-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107010523/http://www.animationmagazine.net/features/shrek-puss-in-boots-rebooting-at-universal-with-chris-meledandri/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年2月26日，確認《鞋貓劍客2》仍在製作中，並由{{le|鮑伯·培斯奇提|Bob Persichetti}}執導<ref name="PIB3">{{cite web |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |title='Puss In Boots 2' In The Works: 'Spider-Verse' Oscar Winner Bob Persichetti Directing |url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/puss-in-boots-2-spider-man-into-the-spider-verse-bob-persichetti-to-direct-1202565786/ |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2019-09-18 |date=2019-02-26 |archive-date=2019-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806044303/https://deadline.com/2019/02/puss-in-boots-2-spider-man-into-the-spider-verse-bob-persichetti-to-direct-1202565786/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年3月17日，宣佈片名更改為《{{lang|en|Puss in Boots: The Last Wish}}》，由《[[古魯家族：新石代|古魯家族：新石代]]》的導演{{le|喬伊·克勞福德 (導演)|Joel Crawford (film director)|喬伊·克勞福德}}執導，{{le|馬克·史威夫特與達米安·香農|Mark Swift and Damian Shannon|馬克·史威夫特}}擔任製片人，並定於2022年9月23日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2021/03/universal-sets-release-dates-for-dreamworks-animation-puss-in-boots-sequel-the-bad-guys-1234716632/|title=DreamWorks Animation’s ‘Puss In Boots’ Sequel & ‘The Bad Guys’ Get Release Dates At Universal|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2021-03-17|accessdate=2021-03-18|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320171554/https://deadline.com/2021/03/universal-sets-release-dates-for-dreamworks-animation-puss-in-boots-sequel-the-bad-guys-1234716632/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Vito Oddo|first=Marco|url=https://collider.com/puss-in-boots-2-sequel-title-release-date-director-details/|title='Puss in Boots 2' Gets an Official Title, Release Date and a New Director|publisher=[[Collider|Collider]]|date=2021-03-17|accessdate=2021-03-18|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320013759/https://collider.com/puss-in-boots-2-sequel-title-release-date-director-details/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《鞋貓劍客2》由[[環球影業|環球影業]]原定於2022年9月23日美國上映<ref>{{cite web|last=Vlessing|first=Etan|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/universal-pictures-sets-release-dates-for-the-bad-guys-puss-in-boots-sequel|title=Universal Pictures Sets Release Dates for 'The Bad Guys,' 'Puss In Boots' Sequel|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2021-03-17|accessdate=2021-03-18|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319183621/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/universal-pictures-sets-release-dates-for-the-bad-guys-puss-in-boots-sequel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2022年4月，電影延期至2022年12月21日美國上映<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2022/04/puss-in-boots-the-last-wish-release-date-1235009625/|title=‘Puss In Boots: The Last Wish’ Heads To Christmas Time|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2022-04-25|accessdate=2022-04-26}}</ref>。

